{"tid":2057344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄羅斯西伯利亞油井大火 俄軍用MT12反坦克炮射擊撲滅","createTime":"2020-06-09T10:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T10:25:04.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3982d03fb127006d62f54799369b4121c70dd726","tid":2057344,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%88%B0%E9%AC%A5%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F-%E5%BC%8F%E6%BB%85%E7%81%AB-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E6%B2%B9%E4%BA%95%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%8D%E5%9D%A6%E5%85%8B%E7%82%AE%E5%B0%84%E6%93%8A%E6%92%B2%E6%BB%85-031608642.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2588%25B0%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%258F-%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%25BB%2585%25E7%2581%25AB-%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E4%25BA%2595%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%259D%25A6%25E5%2585%258B%25E7%2582%25AE%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2592%25B2%25E6%25BB%2585-031608642.html&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XeljUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=b2fbdec5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%88%B0%E9%AC%A5%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F-%E5%BC%8F%E6%BB%85%E7%81%AB-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E6%B2%B9%E4%BA%95%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%8D%E5%9D%A6%E5%85%8B%E7%82%AE%E5%B0%84%E6%93%8A%E6%92%B2%E6%BB%85-031608642.html</a><br />\n俄羅斯8日發表聲明，上月30日在西伯利亞伊爾庫茨克地區的一處油井大火，軍方接獲通知後，立即召集軍官，並運送一架反坦克炮（MT-12 Rapira anti-tank）至事發地點，從距離井口180公尺處發射炮彈以平息火焰，俄羅斯國防部表示發射炮彈滅火有助於設置防噴設備，然後密封油井並滅火。影片可以看到穿著全套軍事防彈衣和頭盔、口罩的士兵，安裝炮彈發射。發生大火的油井由伊爾庫茨克石油公司的一家子公司經營，2018年該公司生產了900萬噸石油和天然氣凝析油。"},{"pid":"7665fe54fdf2f58d467e4b4c198921135b4bbf09","tid":2057344,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T10:01:14.000Z","msg":"天照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e72c356d93ac3f272c09334c98281a1e8e380d9","tid":2057344,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0